expand.user:
Given a node in a mind map with label "{node_label}" and context "{context}",
generate 2-4 relevant sub-points or child nodes.

Respond ONLY with valid JSON in this format:
{
    "children": [
        {"label": "Sub-point 1"},
        {"label": "Sub-point 2"},
        {"label": "Sub-point 3"}
    ]
}

Return only the JSON, no additional text.
